Rosenfarbene 
<normalizedToken id="0B9D61770273F88AB77D36A3F3434281" originalValue="Gänsekresse" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Gaensekresse</normalizedToken>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="F1A08EB729B7245D7B8E0B3FA449C616" pageId="null" pageNumber="231" type="description">
<paragraph id="EBA6CB6031865541FA7738CDEC553AF6" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">
Unterscheidet sich von der nahe verwandten 
<taxonomicName id="B599CD31CDD0A36DF34D834096FA1AF4" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Arabis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="null" pageNumber="231" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="muralis">
<emphasis id="5E99E184130EA78019C35CE3AEFF63AE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">A. muralis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 4) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="709E1FD4D8AECB1A04005F805A2D3914" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">
<normalizedToken id="8F57443297986E343001DC41F2D5A735" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
den Stengel mit gerundeten Zipfeln wenig umfassend; 
<normalizedToken id="66B392BBAC4D0C38D59B937B04152B4A" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
vor der 
<normalizedToken id="A4C96776995F37FD115ACBEA9756DC68" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Bluete</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="C5F66046042C3A2C73CBAF25F27E0459" originalValue="überhängend" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">ueberhaengend</normalizedToken>
;
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="AD6760BDAB2259A9280807497FC3B97F" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
7-10 mm lang, 
<emphasis id="5F7F0A0B82095A0CB3773819193592BE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">purpurn; Griffel 0,8-1,5 mm lang. -</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="B6AEA35775FD883DC81B941C5B50DEDB" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="96B9D92F1828C1C9C1F9FC76F340E0C1" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F5912CEA93613F7D2F60108016A4729B" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">
<emphasis id="0C236725DE39905B330E105F73EC19C8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">
<pageBreakToken id="24D6E2BA10241DFBA695FC21F3B305F1" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Zytologische</pageBreakToken>
Angaben. 2n
</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="C88E0FCE1DC6C7EDA272671994AAADF2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">16:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischem Garten (Jaretzky 1928a).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7E7020E105949FA778B6ED8B84E8BD3D" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">
<emphasis id="EDCB6DFDA33F93153E3538D35CC8CCF4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Felsen und Mauern; in 
<normalizedToken id="F4C6BC64F5B3DFE5B59604A608A1F3EA" originalValue="Süditalien" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Sueditalien</normalizedToken>
nur auf vulkanischem Gestein und Silikatgestein.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="31D14363A0937E0ACEC6A6117FF89135" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">
<emphasis id="90EFF92DD7774C28F49B2B51E207D512" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="A9526CD8AE61ACDC11AD49B8F0AD7438" originalValue="Süditalienische" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Sueditalienische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="1AE734EB0024700D8CB6F5222C2FA1E6" originalValue="Süditalien" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Sueditalien</normalizedToken>
, Sizilien, Sardinien; Tunis (?). - Im Gebiet: Gegend von Neuenburg und Genf, 
<normalizedToken id="A6C6C410B8BB57BA7BFCAAC2034BE541" originalValue="eingebürgert" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">eingebuergert</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="70AE47D856BE43FEF68F2F46A4999ED5" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">
<emphasis id="B2ED0FADE4811631B971BE92FF2E1B43" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Es bleibt 
<normalizedToken id="316ADC5A7E86A75A4DDF719269FEE07E" originalValue="abzuklären" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">abzuklaeren</normalizedToken>
, ob 
<taxonomicName id="E3BE62BBBA47C2737D53ECF13A807B12" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Arabis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="null" pageNumber="231" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosea">
<emphasis id="A16E3E93E591EF19270841A74C737160" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">A. rosea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
identisch ist mit 
<taxonomicName id="16D38C8A23DCFDA979FC46A91DE82AD2" authority="Ten." authorityName="Ten." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Arabis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="null" pageNumber="231" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="collina">
<emphasis id="EC3B64CFE474B1FE2DD79943ABDC8954" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">A. collina</emphasis>
Ten.
</taxonomicName>
, die ebenfalls in 
<normalizedToken id="D44179F009559E389418DFCAAD09ABB7" originalValue="Süditalien" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">Sueditalien</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="297A31D55C003B464280E0BC21BDCFC1" originalValue="wächst" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">waechst</normalizedToken>
aber 
<normalizedToken id="DEE9A8F19ABF9120A69A7E8C70DB92FD" originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">weiss</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="C9E132217E154CE209CCAE8E7355E1A3" originalValue="blühen" pageId="null" pageNumber="231">bluehen</normalizedToken>
soll.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
